o_offer_free_Wii_U_and_Vita_Unreal_Engine_4_code_base_to_devs.php | title = Bloodstained port house Armature to freely offer its UE4 Wii U/Vita code base | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2015-06-09 | accessdate = 2015-06-09 | first = Christian | last = Nutt | archive-date = 2015-06-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150613031431/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/245756/Armature_to_offer_free_Wii_U_and_Vita_Unreal_Engine_4_code_base_to_devs.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>。遊戲的音樂會由曾經為多款《惡魔城》遊戲配樂的前科樂美作曲家[[山根实知琉|山根实知琉]]和另外兩位於Inti Creates工作的音樂總監{{le|山田一法|Ippo Yamada}}與{{le|杰克·考夫曼|Jake Kaufman}}負責<ref name="av club">{{cite web | url = http://www.avclub.com/article/castlevania-director-launches-kickstarter-new-game-219272 | title = Castlevania director launches Kickstarter for new game that’s a lot like his old ones | first = Matt | last = Geraldi | date = 2015-05-11 | accessdate = 2015-05-11 | publisher = [[The_A.V._Club|The A.V. Club]] | archive-date = 2015-05-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150513215715/http://www.avclub.com/article/castlevania-director-launches-kickstarter-new-game-219272 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/iga/bloodstained-ritual-of-the-night/posts/1238140|title=Update 7: $2.5mm, 8-bit tracks + Virt, and a peek into the basement... — Kickstarter|work=kickstarter.com|access-date=2017-07-21|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070947/https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/iga/bloodstained-ritual-of-the-night/posts/1238140|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[2_Player_Productions|2 Player Productions]]就為在[[加州|加州]]北部的[[愛之堡|愛之堡]]取材的五十嵐攝製紀錄片<ref name="polygon day in life"/>，Fangamer則負責為《血污：夜之仪式》的Kickstarter籌募活動作廣告宣傳<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.wired.com/2015/05/bloodstained-kickstarter/ | title = Just Kidding: This Game May Break the Kickstarter Record | first = Chris | last = Kohler | date = 2015-05-28 | accessdate = 2015-05-29 | work = [[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]] | archive-date = 2015-05-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150529041753/http://www.wired.com/2015/05/bloodstained-kickstarter | dead-url = no }}</ref>。另外，在之前的惡魔城系列擔任程序師、總監和設計師的飯田周太郎亦以設計師的身份投入遊戲的製作<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/iga/bloodstained-ritual-of-the-night/posts/1397504|title=October Update: Podcasts, Planners, and Prognosticating|publisher=Kickstarter|date=2015-10-31|accessdate=2017-07-21|archive-date=2017-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170728211543/https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/iga/bloodstained-ritual-of-the-night/posts/1397504|dead-url=no}}</ref>。開發團隊宣佈他們會遵循《[[鏟子騎士|鏟子騎士]]》的做法，以交錯的內容模型方式發行遊戲，這樣可以讓他們準時發佈遊戲的核心內容，並隨著時間推移向遊戲提供額外的內容和避免嚴重的發布延遲<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.destructoid.com/bloodstained-will-take-the-good-shovel-knight-content-delivery-route-not-the-bad-mighty-no-9-one-359774.phtml | title = Bloodstained will take the good Shovel Knight content delivery route, not the bad Mighty No. 9 one | first = Chris | last = Carter | date = 2016-05-07 | accessdate = 2016-05-07 | work = [[Destructoid|Destructoid]] | archive-date = 2016-05-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160508093932/http://www.destructoid.com/bloodstained-will-take-the-good-shovel-knight-content-delivery-route-not-the-bad-mighty-no-9-one-359774.phtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

遊戲的名稱基於女主人公的魔法水晶詛咒，那些水晶以[[花窗玻璃|花窗玻璃]]的形式遍布她的全身，五十嵐認為「血咒」（Bloodstained）對該設計來說是一個很好的形容詞<ref name="gi interview">{{cite web | url = http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2015/05/11/koji-igarashi-explains-the-name-of-his-new-game.aspx | title = Castlevania Mastermind Koji Igarashi Spills Details On Bloodstained | first = Ben | last = Reeves | date = 2015-05-11 | accessdate = 2015-05-12 | work = [[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] | archive-date = 2015-05-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150512155649/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2015/05/11/koji-igarashi-explains-the-name-of-his-new-game.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref>。雖然遊戲的主題以類似於《惡魔城》的[[哥德式藝術|哥德風格]]為基礎，但五十嵐並不想把[[德古拉|德古拉]]的[[公有領域|公有領域]]形象納入其中，原因是他不想讓他的新遊戲感覺像一個「仿傚《惡魔城》的幼稚作品」<ref name="gi interview"/>。除此之外，五十嵐也選擇跟循目前西方市場的電子遊戲趨勢，使米莉亚姆成為強勢的女主角以讓兩性別的玩家都沉醉在遊戲之內，這同時可以免除選擇角色性別的開發負擔<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/244376/Bloodstaineds_female_lead_Miriam_reflects_the_games_audience.php | title = Bloodstained's female lead, Miriam, reflects the game's audience | first = Christian | last = Nutt | date = 2015-05-26 | accessdate = 2015-05-27 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-date = 2015-05-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150529091730/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/244376/Bloodstaineds_female_lead_Miriam_reflects_the_games_audience.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2016年6月14至16日，《血污：夜之仪式》的單層示範版本在[[E3_2016|E3 2016]]供參加者遊玩<ref name="usgamer e32016">{{Cite web | url = http://www.usgamer.net/articles/bloodstained-wins-the-prize-for-e3s-best-thinly-veiled-version-of-an-abandoned-series | title = Bloodstained Wins the Prize for E3's Best Thinly Veiled Version of an Abandoned Series | first = Jeremy | last = Parish | date = 2016-06-17 | accessdate = 2016-06-17 | work = [[US_Gamer|US Gamer]] | archive-date = 2016-06-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160619063908/http://www.usgamer.net/articles/bloodstained-wins-the-prize-for-e3s-best-thinly-veiled-version-of-an-abandoned-series | dead-url = no }}</ref>。一星期後，該示範版本亦發布予曾在Kickstarter上捐款的支持者<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.gamespot.com/articles/bloodstained-ritual-of-the-night-demo-available-to/1100-6441168/ | title = Bloodstained: Ritual of the Night Demo Available to Select Kickstarter Backers | first = Tamoor | last = Hussain | date = 2016-06-23 | accessdate = 2016-06-23 | work = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | archive-date = 2016-06-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160623175834/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/bloodstained-ritual-of-the-night-demo-available-to/1100-6441168/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2016年7月，五十嵐宣布該遊戲已經進入成批生產的階段<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.gamereactor.eu/news/436603/Bloodstained+is+heading+into+full+production/ | title = Bloodstained is "heading into full production" | publisher = Gamereactor | date = 2016-07-20 | accessdate = 2017-07-28 | archive-date = 2017-07-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170728155343/http://www.gamereactor.eu/news/436603/Bloodstained+is+heading+into+full+production/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他原先預計《血污：夜之仪式》在2017年發行，但他在2016年9月宣佈會有第二個工作室幫助開發遊戲，並計劃2018年上半年發布遊戲<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.destructoid.com/bloodstained-ritual-of-the-night-will-now-release-in-2018-385645.phtml | title = Bloodstained: Ritual of the Night will now release in 2018 | first = CJ | last = Andriessen | date = 2016-09-08 | accessdate = 2016-09-08 | work = [[Destructoid|Destructoid]] | archive-date = 2016-09-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160909204721/https://www.destructoid.com/bloodstained-ritual-of-the-night-will-now-release-in-2018-385645.phtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。五十嵐表示延後發行主要是由於多了完成額外募資目標內容所需的工作和完善他在Kickstarter募資時還沒辦法考慮的一個要素，以及他對製作高質量遊戲的承諾。他也說道：「《血污：夜之仪式》要比我以前製作的传统“五十岚魔城”遊戲要來得更好」，他不想為了趕上原本發布日期而草草降低遊戲的質量<ref name="Delay"/>。遊戲完成所需的工時問題以及Inti Create在使用不擅長的虛幻引擎完成五十嵐在遊戲中所要求的一些概念所遭遇的困難，無一不強迫了五十嵐必須得要招募其他工作室加入製作並推遲發佈日期<ref name="Delay">{{cite web | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/10/05/why-bloodstained-was-delayed-to-2018 | title = Why Bloodstained was Delayed to 2018 | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | date = 2016-10-05 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | archive-date = 2016-10-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161006133536/http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/10/05/why-bloodstained-was-delayed-to-2018 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。五十嵐之後透露幫助他的工作室的名字——DICO和Monobit，前者擅長於在地化以及全球性發展，後者負責遊戲引擎的技術援助<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.siliconera.com/2016/11/24/bloodstained-gets-studios-dico-monobit-help-development/ | title = Bloodstained Gets Studios DICO And Monobit To Help Out With Its Development | author = Sato | date = 2016-11-24 | accessdate = 2016-11-24 | work = [[Siliconera|Siliconera]] | archive-date = 2016-11-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161125125417/http://www.siliconera.com/2016/11/24/bloodstained-gets-studios-dico-monobit-help-development/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2017年3月，五十嵐選擇將Wii U的移植計劃轉至[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]，並為受影響的支持者退款或給其選擇第二個平台<ref name="Transition"/>。而在五十嵐開始於Kickstarter籌款時已經設定Wii U為其首要的[[任天堂|任天堂]]移植平台，但當Switch面世後他發現開發團隊很難支持Wii U，所以做出從Wii U轉移至Switch的決定<ref name="Transition">{{cite web | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/03/21/bloodstained-ritual-of-the-night-wii-u-version-canceled-confirmed-for-release-on-nintendo-switch | title = Bloodstained Coming to Nintendo Switch, Canceled on Wii U | first = Evan | last = Campbell | date = 2017-03-21 | accessdate = 2017-03-21 | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | archive-date = 2017-04-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170424091907/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/03/21/bloodstained-ritual-of-the-night-wii-u-version-canceled-confirmed-for-release-on-nintendo-switch | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在2018年8月时，五十岚宣布游戏将延期到2019年发售，并且此前宣布支持的PlayStation Vita平台也将取消开发。<ref>[https://www.polygon.com/2018/8/20/17760030/bloodstained-release-date-delayed-ps-vita-version Bloodstained delayed to 2019, Vita version canceled] {{Wayback|url=https://www.polygon.com/2018/8/20/17760030/bloodstained-release-date-delayed-ps-vita-version |date=20210213060817 }}.Polygon.2018-08-20.[2018-08-21].</ref>12月时，游戏团队确定将取消对[[Mac_OS|Mac OS]]和[[Linux|Linux]]平台的开发计划。<ref>[https://www.gcores.com/articles/105012 官方致歉：《血污 夜之仪式》放弃支持 Mac 和 Linux 平台] {{Wayback|url=https://www.gcores.com/articles/105012 |date=20190820163818 }}.机核网.2018-12-28.[2019-08-21].</ref>《血污：夜之仪式》將交由[[505_Games|505 Games]]發行和銷售<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.usgamer.net/articles/bloodstained-being-published-by-505-games | title = Bloodstained Being Published By 505 Games | first = Mike | last = Williams | date = 2016-10-05 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | work = [[US_Gamer|US Gamer]] | archive-date = 2016-10-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161008141316/http://www.usgamer.net/articles/bloodstained-being-published-by-505-games | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2020年10月，[[网易|网易]]与Artplay宣布将把游戏移植到[[iOS|iOS]]和[[Android|Android]]移动平台，计划于2020年12月4日发售。<ref name="ios&android"/><ref name="mobiledate"/>

